BEAT Privacy Policy

BEAT is a Chrome extension that lets you save and restore SoundCloud sessions to switch between accounts.

Data accessed:
- SoundCloud cookies and site storage (localStorage/sessionStorage) on soundcloud.com.

How it’s used:
- This data is stored locally on your device in chrome.storage.local to enable switching between saved profiles.

What we don’t do:
- We do not transmit any user data off-device.
- We do not sell or share user data with third parties.
- We do not use data for advertising or tracking.

Data retention:
- Stored locally until you delete profiles or uninstall the extension.

Contact:
- send@m.essa.ge
